

                       Agile Method Features/ Properties


1 -	Customer satisfaction
2 -	Welcome change
3 -	Delivery frequently
4 -	Measured by working product
5 -	Attention to excellence
6 -	Simplicity
7 -	Motivated individuals
8 -	Sustainable pace
9 -	Working together daily
10 - Face-to face communication
11 - Self-organizing teams
12 - Reflect and adjust
